title: Gene Healy - Go Directly to Jail - The Criminalization of Almost
description: Gene Healy - Go Directly to Jail - The Criminalization of Almost Everything (pdf) - roflcopter2110 https://extraimage.net/images/2017/12/24/03a9f4f805643c627603981cb3ce9f98.jpg Genre: Judicial System, Criminology Publisher: Cato Institute Language: English ISBN-10: 1930865635 ISBN-13: 978-1930865631 Format: PDF The American criminal justice system is becoming ever more centralized and punitive, owing to rampant federalization and mandatory minimum sentencing guidelines. Go Directly to Jail examines these alarming trends and proposes reforms that could rein in a criminal justice apparatus at war with fairness and common sense
